  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Star Cloak</b> is a <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>accessory</linked> that causes three stars to fall around the player whenever the player takes damage. It consumes no <linked>mana</linked>. The stars that fall cause <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 75 / <linked>150</linked> / <linked>225</linked> / <span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 30 <linked>magic damage</linked> each, pierce through multiple enemies, and pass through <linked>blocks</linked> until reaching the player's altitude, at which point they continue falling until hitting blocks. On <linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked><linked> Desktop</linked>, <linked>[img:Console version]</linked><linked> Console</linked>, and <linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked><linked> Mobile</linked>, the stars have 25 <linked>armor penetration</linked>.",
